quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  26,20,"Muusaa (yo o his) maakani Fir'awna: "Mi warii on gorko hari min ko e majjuɓe ɓen mi jeyaa ado Wahayu arude e am.""
  26,21,"Mi doguno on ɓaawo warugol mo, mi yahi ka saare Madyana, nde mi hulunoo wata on warto lam fii makko, Joomi am okkin mi ganndal, O waɗin mi jeyaaɗo e Nulaaɓe Makko ɓen ɓe O Nulata ɗum faade e yimɓe ɓen."
  26,22,"Ko ne'uɗaa mi kon a maccinɗinaali lam wonndude e maccinɗinngol maaɗa ɓiɗɓe Israa'iila ɓen ɗum ko neema mo wajitirtaa mi ɗum e goonga, kono ɗum haɗataa lam e noddugol ma [ka Diina]."
  26,23,"Fir'awna wi'ani Muusaa (yo o his): "Ko hommbo jeyi tageefooji ɗin, on mo aaƴotoɗaa wonndema an ko a Nulaaɗo makko?!""
  26,24,"Muusaa jaabii Fir'awna o maaki: "Jooma tageefooji ɗin ko Kanko woni Jooma kammuuli ɗin e Jooma leydi ndin, e Jooma ko woni kon hakkunde majji. Si tawii on laatike ko on yananaaɓe wonnde pellet, ko Kanko woni Jooma majji haray rewee Mo Kanko tun."
  26,25,"Fir'awna wi'ani ɓen wonuɓe fee makko immorde e koohooɓe ɓen ka yimɓe makko: "Enee, on jentotaako jaabawol Muusaa ngol, e ko woni kon e makko immorde e aaƴagol fenaande?!""
  26,26,"Muusaa maakani ɓe (yo o his): " Ko Alla woni Joomi mooɗon e Jooma baabiraaɓe mooɗon adinooɓe ɓen.""
  26,27,"Fir'awna wi'i: "Pellet, on aaƴiiɗo wonnde ko o Nulaaɗo faade e mooɗon ko o feetuɗo, o anndaa ko honno o jaaborta, himo wowla kadi ko hakkile jaɓataa.""
  26,28,"Muusaa maaki: "On Alla Mo mi noddata on faade e Muuɗum, ko Kanko woni Jooma funnaange e hirnaange, e Jooma ko woni kon hakkunde majji si tawii no laatanii on hakkillaaji ɗi hakkilirton ɗum"."
  26,29,"Fir'awna wi'ani Muusaa ɓaawo ronkugol makko hujjondirgol e makko: "Mi woondii si a rewii reweteeɗo tanaa am, mami waɗi jeyaaɗo e sokaaɓe ɓen.""
  26,30,"Muusaa (yo o his) maakani Fir'awna: "A waɗay lam jeyaaɗo sokaaɓe ɓen, hay si mi addanii ma ko ɓannginta goongugol am e ko mi addan maa kon immorde ka Alla?""
  26,31,"O wi'i: "Addu ko jaŋtiɗaa kon wonnde no tinndini e goongugol maaɗa si a laatike ko e goonguɓe ɓen jeyaɗaa, e nder kon ko nodditiɗaa ɗum"."
  26,32,"Muusaa werlii tuggordu makko ndun ka leydi, e juhayee, ndu waylii biidaane ɓannguɗo wonannde yi'ooɓe ɓen."
  26,33,"O naadi junngo makko ngon ka jiiba makko tawi ngo wonaa ranewo, o yaltini ngo ko ngo ranewo, ndaneeri jalbeendi wanaa ndaneeri culɗugol, ndaarooɓe ɓen no seedora ngo non."
  26,34,"Fir'awna wi'ani koohooɓe yimɓe makko, ɓen wonu ɓe baŋŋe makko: "Pellet, oo gorko ko mbileejo annduɗo mbilewu"."
  26,35,"Himo faandori mbilewu makko ngun yaltinngol on ka leydi mooɗon. Ko honɗum woni feere mooɗon nde haanuɗen jogaade fii makko?"
  26,36,"Ɓe wi'ani mo: "Nennan mo nennaa kotoo makko kadi, wata yaccor leptugol ɓe, nulu ka ca'e Misra muuɓayɓe mbileeɓe ɓen"."
  26,37,"Yoɓe addane kala mbileejo annduɗo mbilaaku ngun."
  26,38,"Fir'awna mooɓi mbileeɓe makko ɓen fii jippirgol e Muusaa e nder nokkuure anndaa nde e jamaanu hettaaɗo."
  26,39,"Yimɓe ɓen wi'anaa: "Taw si onon ko on mooɓotooɓe fii yo on yi'u fooluɗo on, e hara ko Muusaa kaa ko mbileeɓe ɓen?""